snippet.title: Trailer - Carrot Overload
snippet.description:
project in dev time @t Galoxyum

discover carrot overload the new video game from galoxyum
playable in english and french languages

it is all public,playable with a gamepad


the game price will evolve accordingly to seasons (amount of content so.)
first release : season 1 (may the 11th)
second release : season 2 (september 2025)
3rd release : season 3 (december 2025)
all separated of 3 month and all having additional content included

each season will be sold separately
